    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>在这个游戏中，在每个元素都可以产生新元素的世界中释放你的创造力。</strong>玩耍、组合并发现大量的组合，每种组合都有带来意想不到的转变的潜力。你的创造力是推动这个宇宙发展、解锁成就以及让你的发现变为现实的关键。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3262420/extras/529ecaf84520f64b44c41f745047b13b.avif?t=1737052911\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3262420/extras_big/529ecaf84520f64b44c41f745047b13b.avif?t=1737052911 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>当您深入这个沙盒环境时，探索元素之间的相互作用并享受尝试新想法的乐趣</strong>。没有预先确定的路径：冒险完全掌握在您的手中，每次会话都提供了揭示新的可能性和奥秘的机会。每项成就都会解锁额外的见解，丰富您的经验，让您更接近掌控这个世界。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3262420/extras/5f1e40da80d1a9ba1a5f6b2b0217a7bb.poster.avif?t=1737052911\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3262420/extras/5f1e40da80d1a9ba1a5f6b2b0217a7bb.webm?t=1737052911\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3262420/extras/5f1e40da80d1a9ba1a5f6b2b0217a7bb.mp4?t=1737052911\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>但要小心：每种组合都有其后果。</strong>有些动作可能会触发意想不到的事件，从而显着改变游戏。当你操纵元素时，请注意某些组合可能会破坏你的世界的平衡。准备好接受挑战了吗？</p>",
